Ask me 3 reasons why I love you and imma tell you 6

Keeping my mind, heart, vessel, spirit & soul preciously fed 🍒

As my birthday approaches this Friday, I’ve been reflecting upon my life throughout the past 5 years. 

I’ve experienced immense gut wrenching pain and all the while my heart has only expanded. I’m full of life and more love. I’ve been mentally and emotionally cut open without a single regret to spare. I’ve shed my skin more times than I can count but my heart has kept the score. 

I continue to come out of every “death” better, stronger and wiser than before. Each precious aspect of existing has carried me along my journey thus far. I’m grateful for all that I am and I gently send a kiss to all that I’ve “lost”. 

Where there’s a will this bitch will always find a way ♊️

I felt so beautiful and precious on my birthday yesterday. To be in this blessed skin means everything to me. I’m entering my 30’s as a brighter, wiser and sweeter bitch. 6/16 is one of my favorite days because it comes with so much growth and ease. I haven’t felt like myself in quite some time now and I believe that’s because I was shedding my skin and becoming anew 🌹. I’m so excited to continue meeting my heart and who I am. I love this freak ♊️💋

I’ve been coming into my own more and more beautifully as the days grow on. My Saturn return has been blessing me as it weeds out what isn’t meant for my destiny. I’m grateful for every obstacle and turn. This Gemini found herself all over again in this month of June through and through. My growth is 1 of the sweetest continuous blessings.

Shot by @darrinbaldridge
